snippet.title: My Horse Club : On the Trail of the Mysterious Appaloosa : Wii (Horse Game)
snippet.description: My Horse Club : On the Trail of the Mysterious Appaloosa, gameplay from the german Wii version of the game, emulated for PC, with a lot of graphic bugs and sound issues.
